{
  "stem": "7282.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was the situation?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You told me that you were a little boy when your father passed away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So how did your mother manage?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I told you before, the brothers took over--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the factory.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factory-- I mean, the shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still went to school there in a public school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Coming home from school, when I was younger, I used to-- I used to go in cheder for the whole day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Coming in the evenings, I used to have to make homework to school, to the public school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and that-- and that-- and that's all what it was, what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was, except Shepa was married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that I time, nobody was married-- when my father passed away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody was married then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everybody was at home, or what.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he passed away, I mean, they took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they run the business, or what.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, when they got married, all of them, but I left-- the only one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, well, I mean, I, I finished public school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to cheder after 13 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I went here in yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I start to work in the business, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when all the brothers and sisters married-- so I left with one brother, Nuson, the youngest-- the oldest from me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- so we, we used to work together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he got married, I took over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took over by myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was then maybe, I don't know, 18 years old or-- and so-- and I got to support my mother my sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sister wasn't well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I took it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
